463
00:23:49,166 --> 00:23:50,750
- ( exclaims )

464
00:23:53,625 --> 00:23:55,166
SORRY.

465
00:23:59,125 --> 00:24:00,333
- MY CUTLETS.

466
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:04,041
- I'M UP.

467
00:24:16,625 --> 00:24:19,625
- I'M ON THE WAY, MINAMI,
HIMEJI, WHOEVER.

468
00:24:23,416 --> 00:24:24,666
- WHAT'S GOING ON?

469
00:24:26,625 --> 00:24:28,708
- NO WAY.  HOW'D YOU KNOW
