470
00:24:28,791 --> 00:24:32,166
- ( yells )

471
00:24:36,500 --> 00:24:39,125
HIMEJI.  MINAMI.

472
00:24:41,125 --> 00:24:43,083
- HEY, AKI.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

473
00:24:43,166 --> 00:24:45,500
HIMEJI AND MINAMI
ARE STILL AT THE CAFE.

474
00:24:45,583 --> 00:24:47,500
- HIDEYOSHI, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

475
00:24:47,583 --> 00:24:49,500
- THEY SAID THEY WANTED
TO PLAY WITH ME.

476
00:24:49,583 --> 00:24:51,583
I LIKE GAMES,
SO I FIGURED, WHY NOT?

477
00:24:51,666 --> 00:24:53,833
- SAID THEY WANTED
TO PLAY WITH YOU, HUH?

478
00:24:55,458 --> 00:24:57,333
- I HATE MY LIFE.

479
00:24:57,416 --> 00:24:59,333
- Fukuhara: AND THAT CONCLUDED
THE FIRST DAY

480
00:24:59,416 --> 00:25:01,333
OF THE REFRESHING FESTIVAL
FOR THE SCHOOL YEAR.

481
00:25:03,208 --> 00:25:05,333
- DID WE MAKE
ANYTHING TODAY OR--?

482
00:25:05,416 --> 00:25:07,625
- WHOA, AFTER WE
PAY EVERYTHING OFF,

483
00:25:07,708 --> 00:25:09,916
WE HAVE EXACTLY ENOUGH
TO BUY NEW DESKS.

484
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:12,375
- REALLY?

485
00:25:12,458 --> 00:25:15,125
- HOLD ON.  WHAT ARE THESE
HUGE SALES FROM?

486
00:25:15,208 --> 00:25:17,125
- WOW, THAT'S A LOT.

487
00:25:17,208 --> 00:25:19,125
OVER 500 SOLD,

488
00:25:19,208 --> 00:25:21,875
"PHOTO COLLECTION 'A'
OF EXCLUSIVE SHOOT"

489
00:25:21,958 --> 00:25:23,666
BY KOUTA TRADING
AND COMPANY.

490
00:25:23,750 --> 00:25:26,208
- ALL SOLD OUT,
LIMITED EDITION.

491
00:25:26,291 --> 00:25:29,208
- WELL, IN ANY CASE,
TODAY WAS A TOTAL SUCCESS.

492
00:25:29,291 --> 00:25:32,291
- PRINCESS PEA HEAD, CONGRATS.
I'M PROUD OF YOU.

493
00:25:32,375 --> 00:25:34,166
- AWW, THANKS.
YOU TOO, HAZUKI.

494
00:25:34,250 --> 00:25:36,625
YOU HELPED US OUT A LOT TODAY.
WE REALLY APPRECIATE IT.

495
00:25:36,708 --> 00:25:38,666
- YEAH, A LOT OF THOSE SALES
WERE BECAUSE OF OUR

496
00:25:38,750 --> 00:25:42,000
HOT WAITRESSES TOO.  YOU GUYS
WERE THE MAIN ATTRACTION.

497
00:25:42,083 --> 00:25:44,583
- ALL RIGHT,
THE VOTES HAVE BEEN COUNTED.

498
00:25:44,666 --> 00:25:47,583
SO I CHECKED THEM TWICE TO MAKE
SURE, AND THE WINNER IS...

499
00:25:58,416 --> 00:26:00,583
- I'M NOT TRYING TO BE
A BAD SPORT.

