- THIS IS SO EMBARRASSING.

501
00:26:03,541 --> 00:26:05,416
HOW DO I EXPLAIN THIS
TO MY SELF-ESTEEM?

502
00:26:07,208 --> 00:26:08,916
- FIRST PLACE.
GOOD JOB, MAN.

503
00:26:09,000 --> 00:26:11,041
I KNOW THAT DOESN'T HAPPEN
VERY OFTEN.

504
00:26:11,125 --> 00:26:14,708
- EVERYTHING'S WRONG HERE!
- STOP THE FUN!

505
00:26:14,791 --> 00:26:17,791
LISTEN, TURDLINGS.
THIS IS VERY IMPORTANT.

506
00:26:17,875 --> 00:26:20,833
I WENT TO TALK TO THE PRINCIPAL
TODAY ABOUT YOUR EQUIPMENT.

507
00:26:20,916 --> 00:26:23,291
SHE SAID SHE'LL CONSIDER THIS
A SPECIAL CASE

508
00:26:23,375 --> 00:26:24,791
AND WILL ALLOW YOU
TO USE YOUR PROFIT.

509
00:26:24,875 --> 00:26:28,250
- ( cheering )

510
