00:26:31,416 --> 00:26:33,333
THERE WILL BE
A SUMMONER TEST TOURNAMENT

512
00:26:33,416 --> 00:26:34,958
ON THE SECOND DAY
OF THE FESTIVAL.

513
00:26:35,041 --> 00:26:36,958
THE ONLY TEAM WHO WILL BE
ALLOWED TO PURCHASE

514
